# wiz3D modification: ship the pre-built MinHook libs so contributors get
# clone-and-build without needing to build MinHook separately first. The
# upstream patterns above broadly exclude every lib/ + Release/ folder;
# carve out just the two .lib files wiz3D actually links against.
!build/VC17/lib/
!build/VC17/lib/Release/
!build/VC17/lib/Release/libMinHook.x86.lib
!build/VC17/lib/Release/libMinHook.x64.lib
Ankh.NoLoad
*.VC.db
.vs/

